<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>Could someone go through, from start to finish, the steps of getting the Soulfire. My paladin is only level 18 right now, but I'd just like to know how to do it so i can start getting ready. Thanks for your help.</font></td></tr></table>
